>>>>>>
>>>>>> SOCK_NONBLOCK
>>>>>> SOCK_CLOEXEC
>>>>>>
>>>>>> While there's not any overlap here, that is mostly by chance I 
>>>>>> think. A
>>>>>> cleaner separation is needed here, what happens if some other 
>>>>>> accept4(2)
>>>>>> flag is enabled and it just happens to be the same as
